Detailed Description

cvmx_l2d_fsyn0

L2D_FSYN0 = L2 Failing Syndrome [OW0,4 / OW1,5]

Description: L2 Data ECC SEC/DED Failing Syndrome for lower cache line

Notes: When L2D_SEC_ERR or L2D_DED_ERR are set, this field contains the failing L2 Data ECC 10b syndrome. (A DED Error will always overwrite a SEC Error SYNDROME and FADR).
